                  br
                  p Disneyland patrons were left with extraordinary views of a seemingly unreal smoky orange sky, painted by yet another Californian wildfire. The happiest place on earth is filled will the surreal feeling of doom and destruction.
                  blockquote.instagram-media.mx-auto(data-instgrm-version='7', style=' background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);')
